  "reasoning": "The student shows mostly correct understanding of essay structure (PEEL, integrating context, and using counterarguments) and asks sensible clarifying questions. However, they still rely on a rigid 'formula' and are unsure how to integrate context and counterargument depth, indicating some remaining gaps."
}

